## 📈 Scalability: Honest Assessment

| Scenario | Works Now? | What's Needed |
|---|---|---|
| 1 factory, 1–50k batches, 1–5 users | ✅ Yes | Nothing |
| 5 factories, separate data | ✅ Yes (separate sessions) | Better isolation |
| 50 factories, shared platform (SaaS) | ❌ No | Multi-tenant DB + user isolation |
| Live IoT / sensor streaming | ❌ No | MQTT/Kafka + streaming ingest |
| Mobile app for floor operators | ❌ No | FastAPI backend + React Native / PWA |
| 500k+ row datasets | ❌ Slow | Polars/DuckDB instead of Pandas |
| Government cloud deployment | ⚠️ Partial | Containerize (Docker), add HTTPS |

**Verdict:** Scales well for hackathon and pilot deployments. Needs re-architecture for national-scale SaaS. The good news — the core logic (optimizer, golden signature, feature engineering) is **completely independent** of the UI layer, making it easy to wrap in FastAPI later.

