## 🌍 Real-World Problem: Is It Genuinely Solved?

### ✅ The Problem Is Real and Massive

**What AGPO targets:**
> "Manufacturing SMEs across ALL industries waste 15–40% energy per production cycle because they have no systematic way to discover and replicate their best-ever batch conditions."

**Scale of problem in India:**
- **63 million MSMEs** in manufacturing sector
- Average energy waste: 20–35% vs. optimized operations
- Total energy bill of Indian manufacturing: ~₹8 lakh crore/year
- Even 5% improvement = **₹40,000 crore/year in savings** nationally
- Carbon equivalent: ~50 million tonnes CO₂/year reduction potential

### ✅ Industries AGPO Can Serve (with adaptive pipeline)

| Industry | Key Signals | What AGPO Optimizes |
|---|---|---|
| **Textile** | Loom speed, yarn tension, temperature | Defect rate, throughput, energy per metre |
| **Food Processing** | Temp, humidity, conveyor speed, batch time | Yield, quality grade, energy per tonne |
| **Automotive Parts** | Press force, RPM, cycle time, defect % | Dimensional tolerance, cycle efficiency |
| **Electronics PCB** | Solder temp, flow rate, conveyor speed | First-pass yield, defect PPM, energy |
| **Chemical / Specialty** | Reactor temp, pressure, flow, time | Conversion rate, purity, energy/kg |
| **Ceramics / Glass** | Kiln temp, pressure, duration | Defect rate, energy/unit, colour consistency |
| **Plastics / Rubber** | Barrel temp, screw RPM, mould pressure | Cycle time, dimensional accuracy, waste |

### ⚠️ What Still Prevents Full Real-World Deployment

1. **No live data input** — factory operators won't export Excel manually every day
2. **No alerting** — when a batch goes Red Zone, no one is notified automatically
3. **Demo data is one industry** — funding committee will ask "show me textile / food"
4. **No baseline comparison** — can't show "before AGPO vs after AGPO" without pilot data

